{"tid":2072334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉巧琦批評由特首指派法官處理國安法案件等同「人治」","createTime":"2020-06-20T13:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T05:51:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1a695f659db6db29a7cc178004da84b4fb88c997","tid":2072334,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:34:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533201-20200620.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533201-20200620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=20546fd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533201-20200620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6ab71955\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533201-20200620.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港區國安法草案規定香港特區設立國家安全委員會，委員會內設立國家安全事務顧問，由中央政府指派；律政司亦要設立專門檢控部門，負責國家安全犯罪案件的檢控工作。<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會副主席葉巧琦說，如果律政司處理國安案件的部門需要向「國家安全事務顧問」徵詢意見或接受提點，憂慮律政司既有的司法獨立刑事檢控程序和準則，會受到「國家安全事務顧問」的外來影響。<br />\n<br />\n葉巧琦批評，由行政長官指派法官負責處理危害國家安全案件，對香港的司法獨立破壞相當大，等同是「人治」，質疑只是指派「聽話」的法官處理相關案件。她說，法官只會按法律原則審理案件，沒有理由由司法機構以外的某一個人，指定某一個法官才能審理某一類案件，破壞一直以來、行之有效由終審法院首席法官，根據法律才能指派法官的制度。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中央在香港設立的「駐港國家安全公署」在特定情形下對極少數危害國家安全案件行使管轄權。葉巧琦認為，有關寫法並不清晰，質疑草案未有介定何為「極少數」，「公署」是否受香港法律規管，所指的「管轄權」是否包括執法權等。"},{"pid":"79cca49aad50f1baca2e2b44027d4737926556cb","tid":2072334,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"本身法庭啲官都係咁樣做法<br />\n根本香港所謂法治就唔存在"},{"pid":"c88dacfb69af524657ad2b032bf1bdb6d0f50498","tid":2072334,"uid":244818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"借個位 立會事實處 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072298</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992602f1f4582c28b5432ce958a71d350537d610","tid":2072334,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"張舉能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知邊撚個投贊成呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf5cf31ae6bbd002d55d375799cae7893a71dae","tid":2072334,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"大律師公會班法治撚仲典下典下好嬲好嬲"},{"pid":"d425bf1713d35c255a68b037b81d58a0e6bd4d4a","tid":2072334,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"992602f1f4582c28b5432ce958a71d350537d610","tid":2072334,"uid":308251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"張舉能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知邊撚個投贊成呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"張舉撚點黑哨大律師都仲搵到錢<br />\n由特首指派法官處理國安法案件, 根本唔可能比香港律師跟case"},{"pid":"5924a45d8a739cb559c2b228eb5d5b46ca0c8f99","tid":2072334,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf5cf31ae6bbd002d55d375799cae7893a71dae","tid":2072334,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"大律師公會班法治撚仲典下典下好嬲好嬲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"好似香港司法制度本身完全無事咁"},{"pid":"1d2ab803a59a39f5e1b90e595a9d876768341992","tid":2072334,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5924a45d8a739cb559c2b228eb5d5b46ca0c8f99","tid":2072334,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf5cf31ae6bbd002d55d375799cae7893a71dae","tid":2072334,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"大律師公會班法治撚仲典下典下好嬲好嬲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"好似香港司法制度本身完全無事咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"就算紅官狂屈人坐監<br />\nunder香港司法制度班律師大把錢袋<br />\n平時就連法援case